{"tid":162020,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[三大偵探]金田一一，柯南，L，實力應該點排？","createTime":"2017-03-19T03:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T01:28:45.000Z","uid":34701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"be229ca76fdd046a1de7f0fbfed9d23393eeadba","tid":162020,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:17:23.000Z","msg":"自己最鍾意L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開始佢唔使現身都已經知奇拿身處日本，是咪最勁嗰個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nL&gt;金田一=柯南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0156caec694247f228180c2048bd1fba7ef434b9","tid":162020,"uid":70212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"好難比較，你講 L 嘅情况好 depend on information availability, 如果金田一或者柯南有 L 嘅 information source 應該都做到<br />\n<br />\n題外話：死神能力一定係柯南最勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b8eb262960aa580eb1921cb4642e4866a02f55","tid":162020,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好難比較，你講 L 嘅情况好 depend on information availability, 如果金田一或者柯南有 L 嘅 information source 應該都做到<br />\n<br />\n題外話：死神能力一定係柯南最勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都要有返咁上下推理能力先得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果比較推理能力呢？你哋點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0951c5650097df38a78d57f46ba52c2f0f83150f","tid":162020,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:44:22.000Z","msg":"如果用死亡率去計<br />\n<br />\n其實L應該算死得最少人"},{"pid":"0cfa517fe3cbe99930dcd88b6dc577364863f3de","tid":162020,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:45:44.000Z","msg":"亞視：金田一<br />\n無線：柯南，L"},{"pid":"b0d05e0504272461976492ed0a016b0629535163","tid":162020,"uid":62040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:48:46.000Z","msg":"呢個問題同 悟空 埼玉 嗚人 邊個好抽d 有異曲同工之妙<br />\n不如講下邊套作品既表達手法有趣d 好過啦"},{"pid":"5421c4557fc1c686cee04a5401440db311c1051a","tid":162020,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:04:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個問題同 悟空 埼玉 嗚人 邊個好抽d 有異曲同工之妙<br />\n不如講下邊套作品既表達手法有趣d 好過啦</blockquote><br />\n老師一定係最少頭髮"},{"pid":"1a4068dde9af5368987ccfd53a1cb6a851ff3ace","tid":162020,"uid":34701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:18:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個問題同 悟空 埼玉 嗚人 邊個好抽d 有異曲同工之妙<br />\n不如講下邊套作品既表達手法有趣d 好過啦</blockquote><br />\n我記得有個case係有架lift原本可以唔知載幾多人，但次次載到上限減一人就已經超載，之後發現原來有條屍喺lift頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個好似係柯南嘅故事嚟，覺得超恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1db86b2dfad91621d2a4b381c705221a987babc","tid":162020,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"QED證明終了 同 CMB森羅博物館事件目錄<br />\n呢兩套都收上面嗰幾套皮啦"},{"pid":"770112e444a644b6d45c2b1ec3e583c7d6a1a1ff","tid":162020,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果用死亡率去計<br />\n<br />\n其實L應該算死得最少人</blockquote><br />\nL要同死神鬥，而金田一同柯南本身就係死神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78ff63bd9b9a02096bac6cef52571a63b0cc3ae","tid":162020,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"柯南其實好蠢，佢故事入面有幾個人推理都勁過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367b628113cca468d6c9749e6dcf6faaf1327e84","tid":162020,"uid":12343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:31:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個問題同 悟空 埼玉 嗚人 邊個好抽d 有異曲同工之妙<br />\n不如講下邊套作品既表達手法有趣d 好過啦</blockquote><br />\n我記得有個case係有架lift原本可以唔知載幾多人，但次次載到上限減一人就已經超載，之後發現原來有條屍喺lift頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個好似係柯南嘅故事嚟，覺得超恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有印象 <br />\n但咁都諗到 幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355d3557fea68d097b7e38a51ad3c2b4ff03fc61","tid":162020,"uid":19947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柯南其實好蠢，佢故事入面有幾個人推理都勁過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係單純<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/152526_4704b12a4eef7ed0a8817a02a1bb8542.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F152526_4704b12a4eef7ed0a8817a02a1bb8542.jpg&h=c8798a31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3a96df6d7c87463dffc5c534460c6da3884902f","tid":162020,"uid":51977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:50:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>QED證明終了 同 CMB森羅博物館事件目錄<br />\n呢兩套都收上面嗰幾套皮啦</blockquote><br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1187c63a51d2aacdf60a3728f8e59b87b24210","tid":162020,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"柯南最勁係佢老豆啲知識同博士啲研究<br />\n<br />\n金田一一同L唔係好識比，但兩個都勁過柯南就一定"},{"pid":"b22a20fb95c7f7013d0679ffa9cb2a1ac900ac8a","tid":162020,"uid":81598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:21:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柯南最勁係佢老豆啲知識同博士啲研究<br />\n<br />\n金田一一同L唔係好識比，但兩個都勁過柯南就一定</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又冇得咁講既, 佢都係變細左先要用博士既研究,<br />\n如果佢仲係新一, 實力同金田一係相對"},{"pid":"c271672a3850e71006827a9b87ced45a186f3ba6","tid":162020,"uid":81598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:25:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柯南其實好蠢，佢故事入面有幾個人推理都勁過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係因為個世界觀太大姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人物多到數唔晒,<br />\n佢老豆比佢好, 係勝在經驗豐富,<br />\n同埋柯南/新一識太多對破案有用既野,<br />\n絕對音感, 又識渣飛機, 識渣船, 識渣槍, 乜春都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3ad5d87589c75151d01d016f4ae650c8fb0689","tid":162020,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:26:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>柯南最勁係佢老豆啲知識同博士啲研究<br />\n<br />\n金田一一同L唔係好識比，但兩個都勁過柯南就一定</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又冇得咁講既, 佢都係變細左先要用博士既研究,<br />\n如果佢仲係新一, 實力同金田一係相對</blockquote><br />\n佢啲腰帶同足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6143a6b15c0a799edf0a5fb570c7bc8d1dc3d1","tid":162020,"uid":81598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:37:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>柯南最勁係佢老豆啲知識同博士啲研究<br />\n<br />\n金田一一同L唔係好識比，但兩個都勁過柯南就一定</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又冇得咁講既, 佢都係變細左先要用博士既研究,<br />\n如果佢仲係新一, 實力同金田一係相對</blockquote><br />\n佢啲腰帶同足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以話如果計係新一, 冇用博士d研究, 同金田一會係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n金田一可能推理能力比新一高, 但佢識做既野金田一又唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫做打番個和, 不過佢地兩個個IQ都係一樣160"},{"pid":"bb571efa94dba8f0c1ea73a16942c2ea1726f4a3","tid":162020,"uid":81598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:44:43.000Z","msg":"不過其實L都好難話有幾勁,<br />\n始終故事上唔太突然到佢果種要自己出去搵證據, 分析同各種能力,<br />\n同金田一同柯南比係有d出入,"},{"pid":"741cd31ddbe2389be06c54c4c363be140ed0126b","tid":162020,"uid":53252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:45:47.000Z","msg":"單純計人物唔計故事<br />\n我覺得金田一比柯南/新一寫實好多"},{"pid":"f6151085ee8af22da220ac29ae24364388375e53","tid":162020,"uid":81598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:52:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單純計人物唔計故事<br />\n我覺得金田一比柯南/新一寫實好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 青山寫得新一太完美, <br />\n除左唱歌難聽之外樣樣都掂"},{"pid":"d24fd826141f5b33ebc4a5d9864d447138dd03f5","tid":162020,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:23:05.000Z","msg":"你係咪打錯字?<br />\n應該係金田一, 柯南, 夜神月, 實力點排"},{"pid":"ac2dedac2e33f2c31f3235da35f4c81808b7f506","tid":162020,"uid":29950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>單純計人物唔計故事<br />\n我覺得金田一比柯南/新一寫實好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 青山寫得新一太完美, <br />\n除左唱歌難聽之外樣樣都掂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起同two mix crossover個集"},{"pid":"910a48974c9bd4cc4cb44592ed716a341835ab6f","tid":162020,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪打錯字?<br />\n應該係金田一, 柯南, 夜神月, 實力點排</blockquote><br />\n夜神月本身都唔係唔係偵探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢三個係日本三大名偵探丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}